
Rules for BattleShip

Each player selects an area to place their ships, whether in horizontal or
vertical. 
If a player strikes a spot in the grid that contains a part of the ship, 
an '3' will be displayed in order to mark the hit zone
If a player misses, the spot will be left untouched.
Inputs are taken by ROW first followed by COLUMN


Good luck, have fun!!
Press 1 to return to Main Menu
